title: Hour 1 - NBA Western Conference Finals Game 5, 3-Pointers Or Bust
itunes:title: Hour 1 - NBA Western Conference Finals Game 5, 3-Pointers Or Bust
description:
Dan was not surprised to see the Dallas Mavericks take a game from the Warriors but would be if they manage to get another one. And he talks about the prevalence of 3-point shooting and how it has affected today's NBA.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
